---
title: Fajita-Style Protein Shred Bowls with Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, quick and packed with flavour, this dish delivers the fiesta without any fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair beautifully with tender protein shreds to create a fajita bowl that comes together with smoky Mexican-style seasoning.
